data.description: Come and see this beautiful model-like home loaded with upgrades.... Home is like new and is beautiful inside and out.  It will not last!!! This 4-bedroom two bath home has a nice open floor plan and is move in ready loaded with everything that you need to make you feel like you are right at home. This home has an upgraded kitchen, quartz counter tops, back splash, a large island, beautiful lighting, all stainless-steel appliances, a disposal, dishwasher and large tile flooring in all the wet areas. The master bedroom is carpeted and is very spacious, it also has a huge walk-in closet. Master bath has a double sink, walk in shower/tub and a separate toilet room. All bedrooms are carpeted and are a nice size. This home has sliding glass doors and plenty of natural lighting. Enjoy a nice sized backyard that is partially fenced with no backyard neighbors. Come out and see for yourself you want regret it! If you enjoy the beach style living, just a few minutes away is the beautiful Southshore Bay Lagoon! Vista Palms Community is located close to I-75 and 301, minutes to sugar sand beaches, shopping, restaurants, Walmart, Publix, Aldi, hospitals, and More. This is a Great location! It is also located near several major hospitals.   The Vista Palms community has some great amenities including a resort-style swimming pool, cabanas, splash pad for the littles ones, nature trails, pickle ball, a hot tub and a fitness center. Don't delay schedule your appointment and come see for yourself!
